   Hence LHS = ##z |1| n
             = ##z |0| n           by poly_one_eq_poly_zero
             = #0z                 by ring_add_group, group_id_exp
             = |0|                 by poly_mod_ring_property
         RHS = chop [##n]
             = chop [#0]           by IN_SING, ring_num_element
             = |0|                 by poly_chop_const_zero
