   By induction on p.
   Base case: poly [] ==> (evalz (lift []) (q % z) = poly_eval (PolyRing r) (lift []) q % z)
   LHS = evalz (lift []) (q % z)
       = evalz [] (q % z)     by poly_lift_of_zero
